<subSubSection pageId="141" pageNumber="742" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="141.[1448,2657,1122,1667]" pageId="141" pageNumber="742">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1450,1801,1516,1550]" pageId="141" pageNumber="742">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Vulnerable on The IUCN Red List. The Western Vlei Rat has a restricted distribution that is declining in area, extent, and quality of habitat.
</paragraph>
